WEBVTT

00:00:10.698 --> 00:00:18.831 line:90% position:50% align:center
Jehovah loves clean people.
He made the earth so clean.

00:00:19.540 --> 00:00:26.213 line:90% position:50% align:center
I can bring him so much joy
when I put away my toys.

00:00:26.213 --> 00:00:35.431 line:90% position:50% align:center
Jehovah loves clean people.
That’s why I love to clean!

00:00:40.686 --> 00:00:49.236 line:90% position:50% align:center
Jehovah loves clean people.
He wants us to be clean.

00:00:49.236 --> 00:00:56.076 line:90% position:50% align:center
So I’ll go and clean my room;
I can wash some dishes too.

00:00:56.076 --> 00:01:04.376 line:90% position:50% align:center
Jehovah loves clean people.
That’s why I love to clean!

00:01:10.466 --> 00:01:19.516 line:90% position:50% align:center
Jehovah loves clean people.
He’ll help us to be clean.

00:01:19.516 --> 00:01:26.190 line:90% position:50% align:center
Oh, the happiness it brings
when we clean up all our things!

00:01:26.190 --> 00:01:34.782 line:90% position:50% align:center
Jehovah loves clean people.
That’s why I love to clean!

